NK036(chi)012:0: rdzogs pa chen po snying thig spros bcas kyi dbang lce btsun gyis mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK036(chi)012:1: dbang thams cad kyi mnga' bdag rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)012:2: nges pa'i lung la dad pa'i gding rnyed skal ldan bu //
NK036(chi)012:3: 'phangs pa'i srog nor dam pa'i chos la gtong phod can //
NK036(chi)012:4: sbyangs pa'i 'phro can blo yi rtse mor rab tu 'jug pa'i don //
NK036(chi)012:5: dbang rnams kun gyi gnas bsdus nges pa'i don du bdag gis dgrol //
NK036(chi)012:6: tshig gi dbang la bye brag bsam yas kyang gnad kyi man ngag snying po phyung pa ni //
NK036(chi)012:7: spros bcas dbang gi tshig don mthong ba'i don //
NK036(chi)012:8: nges par bsdus la lag len khrigs su bsdeb //
NK036(chi)012:9: de la skal ba mchog dang ldan pa'i slob ma
NK036(chi)012:10: dam tshig rang gi srog bas gces par 'dzin pa
NK036(chi)012:11: gnyis nas bdun tshun chad las de bas mang na
NK036(chi)012:12: mkha' 'gro ma'i chad pa 'ong nges pas bu mchog
NK036(chi)012:13: de rnams la bstan par bya'o de la spros pa
NK036(chi)012:14: la dga' ba rnams kyi dbang nges par bya ba'i
NK036(chi)012:15: tshig gi don 'di la gzhan nas rgya cher bstan
NK036(chi)012:16: kyang de rnams kyis don gyi gnad gtan la mi
NK036(chi)012:17: phebs te dper na lung pa stong pa'i rlung sgra
NK036(chi)012:18: dang 'dra ste don la ma g.yel bas dbang dngos
NK036(chi)012:19: kyi lag khrigs bla ma'i phyag len nyams kyi man
NK036(chi)012:20: ngag dngos min pa'i phyir sems la gab par bya'o
NK036(chi)012:21: de'i don nges pa'i dbang mchog len par 'dod pa'i
NK036(chi)012:22: skal ldan gyis gnad nges pa tshig gsum du rig
NK036(chi)012:23: par bya'o // de la nges pa'i don gyi dbang
NK036(chi)012:24: ni sngon du 'gro ba slob dpon gyi 'brel brtag
NK036(chi)012:25: par bya'o // pa dang gcig / dngos gzhi dbang
NK036(chi)012:26: nges pa'i bya ba lag khrigs kyi go rim bstan
NK036(chi)012:27: par bya'o // pa dang gcig / pa dang gnyis
NK036(chi)012:28: / rjes kyi bya ba rnal 'byor pa'i spyod lam
NK036(chi)012:29: gyi tshul bstan pas nges par bya ba'o //
NK036(chi)012:30: de la dang po slob dpon dang slob ma'i 'brel pa brtag pa la /
NK036(chi)012:31: dang po bla ma'i mtshan nyid bstan pa ni mtshan
NK036(chi)012:32: nyid dang mi ldan na dbang nges pa'i 'bras bu
NK036(chi)012:33: 'byin mi nus pas de'i mtshan nyid mdo rgyud la
NK036(chi)012:34: sogs tshig gi don la nges par sbyangs pa dang
NK036(chi)012:35: gcig / mngon sum don gyi gnas lugs la rtogs pa'i lam sbyong ba dang gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:36: tshogs gnyis la sogs pa bsags pas mthar phyin pa
NK036(chi)012:37: dang rang gi rgyud thog tu smin cing sgo gsum
NK036(chi)012:38: gyis gzhan gyi rgyud smin nus pa'o /
NK036(chi)012:39: slob ma'i mtshan nyid nges pas gdam pa'i snod brtag pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:40: don dam pa'i bla ma la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed pa dang gcig /
NK036(chi)012:41: dad pa'i zhing sa bzang bas mi dge ba'i phyogs dug sbrul ltar spong ba dang gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:42: 'khrul pa'i don rig pas 'jig rten gyi bdog pa la mi chags shing gtong nus pa dang gsum /
NK036(chi)012:43: mdor na lus dang srog thams cad kyang dam pa'i don la blo bsgyur nus pa dang bzhi'o //
NK036(chi)012:44: dngos gzhi dbang nges pa'i lag khrigs la gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:45: bsham pa rdzas kyi rim pa chas su gzhug pa dang gcig /
NK036(chi)012:46: smin bya slob ma'i tshogs nges pa dngos so //
NK036(chi)012:48: gnas khyad par can du dkyil 'khor bsham pa dang gcig /
NK036(chi)012:49: der bsags pa'i rdzas kyi rim pa dgod pa'o //
NK036(chi)012:50: de la dkyil 'khor bsham pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:51: dur khrod la sogs pa dben pa'i gnas su dkyil
NK036(chi)012:52: 'khor 'dom gang gru bzhi pa ba'i rnam lnga dang
NK036(chi)012:53: bdud rtsi lnga yis chag chag 'thor bar byas la
NK036(chi)012:54: / thig dang rdul tshon byin gyis brlab pa spyi dang 'dra /
NK036(chi)012:55: dbus su mthing ka zlum po pad+ma 'dab brgyad phyogs mtshan dang mtshams mdzes tshon du bya /
NK036(chi)012:56: gru chad sgo dang sgo rgyan rta babs rdo rje'i
NK036(chi)012:57: ra ba me ri'i phreng ba 'od zer gyis bskor
NK036(chi)012:58: ba bri'o // gnyis pa bsags pa rdzas kyi bya ba ni /
NK036(chi)012:59: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar rin po che'i bum pa
NK036(chi)012:60: kha dog phyog tshon la rigs lnga'i sa bon +amo
NK036(chi)012:61: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa bris la dgod /
NK036(chi)012:62: kha rgyan mgul rgyan dang bcas pa'i nang du rin
NK036(chi)012:63: po che lnga 'bru lnga sman lnga spos lnga gtsang
NK036(chi)012:64: ma'i chu dang 'o ma la sogs dkar gsum dang
NK036(chi)012:65: / bu ram la sogs pa'i mngar gsum gyis dgang ngo //
NK036(chi)012:66: bum pa lnga'i steng du mda' lnga /
NK036(chi)012:71: rigs lnga'i tsaka li lnga dgod /
NK036(chi)012:72: gsang dbang gi rdzas thod pa bdud rtsis bkang ba yang dgod /
NK036(chi)012:73: dbang gsum pa'i rdzas rig ma mtshan ldan yang bzhag go //
NK036(chi)012:74: gzhan yang sgo bzhir phur pa bzhi /
NK036(chi)012:75: mtshams bzhir ral gri bzhi dgod do //
NK036(chi)012:76: gzhan yang phyi'i mchod pa lnga dang /
NK036(chi)012:79: tshogs kyi mchod pa rgya chen po dang /
NK036(chi)012:80: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong gi gtor ma rgya chen po yang bsham mo //
NK036(chi)012:81: bla bre dang thang sku la sogs pa ci rigs pas gnas brgyan par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:82: smin bya slob ma'i bya ba la gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:83: 'jug par byed pa slob ma'i sngon 'gro dang /
NK036(chi)012:84: byin brlabs kyi byed pa slob dpon gyi las so //
NK036(chi)012:86: dbang gi gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK036(chi)012:87: bla mas gnang ba sbyin zhing /
NK036(chi)012:88: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed 'bogs pa dang gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:89: bsrung ba gdags shing ye shes dbab pa dang gsum /
NK036(chi)012:90: me tog dor zhing ming gdags pa dang bzhi /
NK036(chi)012:91: mig dbye zhing mthong ba bstan pa dang lnga'o //
NK036(chi)012:92: dang po gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:93: e ma hoh skyes chen 'gro mgon bla ma rje //
NK036(chi)012:94: bdag ni las can shes rab bu //
NK036(chi)012:95: gsang bar nges pa'i lung 'di la //
NK036(chi)012:96: gtod pas bdag ni gzung du gsol //
NK036(chi)012:97: zhes lan gsum zhu ba dbul /
NK036(chi)012:98: gnyis pa bla mas rjes gnang sbyin zhing skyabs 'gro sems bskyed 'bogs pa la gsum /
NK036(chi)012:103: e ma ho skal ldan sems kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:104: mchog tu gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK036(chi)012:105: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gi lung //
NK036(chi)012:107: bdag nyid chen po khyod kyis ni //
NK036(chi)012:108: blo yi the tshom rab bsal nas //
NK036(chi)012:109: nor bu'i yon tan mthong ba bzhin //
NK036(chi)012:110: bdag la bla mar spro lags sam //
NK036(chi)012:112: slob mas spro lags zhes brjod do //
NK036(chi)012:114: rang lus 'khor lo bzhi rtsa rlung thig le'i gnas lugs dran par byas la /
NK036(chi)012:115: rlung lnga rnam dag dwangs ma'i sku //
NK036(chi)012:116: nyon mongs rnam dag ye shes lnga //
NK036(chi)012:117: sku gsum mdzad pa mthar phyin pa //
NK036(chi)012:118: dkon mchog gsum la rtogs pas 'dud //
NK036(chi)012:119: ces lan gsum gyi rjes la /
NK036(chi)012:121: gsum pa sems bskyed pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:122: lam gyi snang ba bzhi'i don dran par byas la /
NK036(chi)012:124: e ma ho ma rig mun pa'i klong //
NK036(chi)012:125: rang rig thabs shes sgron ma yi //
NK036(chi)012:126: rang la gnas pa'i ye shes de //
NK036(chi)012:127: bla ma'i drin gyis rtogs par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:128: zhes lan gsum gyi rjes la /
NK036(chi)012:129: smon pa'i don bshad par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:131: e ma ho sangs rgyas mthar thug dbyings rig gnyis //
NK036(chi)012:132: sku gsum ngo bo mtha' bral gzhi //
NK036(chi)012:133: tshig las 'das pa'i rang byung de //
NK036(chi)012:134: da lta nyid du rtogs par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:135: zhes lan gsum brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK036(chi)012:137: bsrung ba gdags shing ye shes dbab pa la gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:138: bsrung ba gdags pa dang ye shes dbab pa'o //
NK036(chi)012:139: dang po tshon sna lnga'i skud pa la /
NK036(chi)012:142: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho &aham /
NK036(chi)012:143: zhes pas sngags mdud byas la /
NK036(chi)012:144: pho'i dpung ba g.yas pa mo'i g.yon pa la gdags so //
NK036(chi)012:145: gnyis pa ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:146: slob ma lus gnad rdo rje skyil krung bca' ru bcug la /
NK036(chi)012:147: 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa yi ge thig le dang /
NK036(chi)012:148: kun bzang yab yum gsal gdab la /
NK036(chi)012:149: steng 'og gi rlung kha sbyar la shes pa ma yengs shig byas /
NK036(chi)012:150: dmigs pa ni tshig don bsam zhing /
NK036(chi)012:151: bla mas d+aa ma ru dkrol zhing 'di skad do //
NK036(chi)012:152: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:153: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ni //
NK036(chi)012:154: sprul pa'i sku yi bzhugs gnas yin //
NK036(chi)012:155: rlung lnga g.yo bcos las 'das pa //
NK036(chi)012:156: thig le 'od skur shigs se shig /
NK036(chi)012:157: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:158: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo ni //
NK036(chi)012:159: chos kyi sku yi bzhugs gnas yin //
NK036(chi)012:160: sangs rgyas rig lnga me re re //
NK036(chi)012:161: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:162: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo ni //
NK036(chi)012:163: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bzhugs gnas yin //
NK036(chi)012:164: mtshan dang dpe byad 'khrugs pa yis //
NK036(chi)012:165: thig le 'od skur ya la la //
NK036(chi)012:166: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:167: spyi bo bde ba'i 'khor lo ni //
NK036(chi)012:168: sku gsum 'dus pa'i bzhugs gnas yin //
NK036(chi)012:170: khro rgyal gad rgyang ya la la //
NK036(chi)012:171: zhes pa de dag gi dmigs pa re mos kyi dbab pa'o //
NK036(chi)012:172: bzhi pa me tog dor zhing ming gdags pa la gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:175: dang po ni dar sna lnga'i spyan dar byas la /
NK036(chi)012:176: thal mo'i bar du bzung ste /
NK036(chi)012:177: mig dar nag pos bkab la /
NK036(chi)012:180: thog ma'i 'od gsal snying po nas //
NK036(chi)012:182: gzhi la sbyangs pa'i las 'bras kyis //
NK036(chi)012:183: rigs mchog de la 'bab par shog /
NK036(chi)012:184: ces pas pho brang gi dbus su dor ro //
NK036(chi)012:185: gnyis pa ming gdags pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:186: dbus su 'bab na sna tshogs rang grol /
NK036(chi)012:187: shar du rdo rje snying po /
NK036(chi)012:189: nub tu bde chen rgyal po /
NK036(chi)012:190: byang du sgo lnga bya bral du gdags so //
NK036(chi)012:191: de nas mig dbye zhing mthong ba bstan pa la gnyis /
NK036(chi)012:195: kye ma rdo rje 'dzin mgon rje //
NK036(chi)012:196: bdag ni khams gsum 'khor bar long //
NK036(chi)012:197: rje yi ye shes thur ma yis //
NK036(chi)012:198: bdag gi ma rig bsal du gsol //
NK036(chi)012:201: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:203: rang la bzhag nas gzhan du btsal //
NK036(chi)012:204: thur ma yid bzhin nor bus mtshon //
NK036(chi)012:205: zhes gser gyi thur mas mig dar bsal la //
NK036(chi)012:206: de dag gi don bshad do //
NK036(chi)012:207: gnyis pa mthong ba bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK036(chi)012:211: de nas mched lcam gyi mthong ba bstan pa'o //
NK036(chi)012:212: de la dang po bla ma'i mthong ba bstan pa ni ltos shig ltos shig rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:213: ma yengs sems kyi nga la ltos //
NK036(chi)012:214: nga la mthong ba sna tshogs pa'o //
NK036(chi)012:215: bu khyod kyis ni cir mthong smros //
NK036(chi)012:217: bu yis bla ma sangs rgyas su mthong lags /
NK036(chi)012:219: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:220: ltos shig mig can skal ldan bu //
NK036(chi)012:222: dad pa'i mchog ni bskyed re ran //
NK036(chi)012:223: khyod kyi dkyil 'khor ci ru mthong //
NK036(chi)012:225: la las dkar po shas che bar mthong /
NK036(chi)012:226: la las dmar po la sogs pa mthong ba 'byung bas /
NK036(chi)012:227: dkyil 'khor gyi de nyid bshad do //
NK036(chi)012:228: de nas rdzas kyi mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:229: e ma lta shes skal ldan bu //
NK036(chi)012:230: brda dang dam rdzas bkod pa'i tshogs //
NK036(chi)012:231: gnas lugs mtshon pa'i rdzas 'di ltos //
NK036(chi)012:232: mthong ba'i don de bdag la smros //
NK036(chi)012:233: zhes pas skal ba dang ldan pa de rnams kyi don ji bzhin nyid du shes so //
NK036(chi)012:234: de nas rdzas kyi de nyid bshad do //
NK036(chi)012:235: de nas mched lcam gyi mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:236: e ma ho ngo mtshar rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:237: grogs kyi dam pa gang yin pa //
NK036(chi)012:238: 'jug sgo gcig pa'i spun grogs la //
NK036(chi)012:239: khyod kyis cir mthong bdag la smros //
NK036(chi)012:240: dag pa'i snang ba mthong re ran //
NK036(chi)012:241: ces pas de nyid kyis mthong ba'i don dri'o //
NK036(chi)012:242: de la dkyil 'khor gyi de nyid bshad pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:243: dbus zlum po mthing khar byung ba ni gzhi chos
NK036(chi)012:244: nyid kyi don la gnyen po dang bral ba'i barda'o
NK036(chi)012:245: // pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad mdzes tshon du byung ba
NK036(chi)012:246: ni gzhi la rlung lnga'i dwangs ma dang ldan pa'i
NK036(chi)012:247: // barda'o // gru chad bzhir byung ba ni 'byung bzhi'i 'od bzhi dang ldan pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:248: khyams sgo bzhi dang bcas pa ni phrin las bzhi po rang la tshang ba'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:249: pad rag gi rtsig pa ni ye shes lnga'i ra ba dang ldan pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:250: rta babs bzhi ni gzhi la tshad med bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:251: 'dod yon gyi lha mo ni 'dod yon ma spangs rgyan du shar ba'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:252: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed ni gzhi'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:253: pha gu ser po ni 'dod dgu rang la 'byung ba'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:254: rdo rje'i rwa ba ni don la 'gyur ba med pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:255: 'od zer phreng bar bskor ba ni sku lnga ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:256: gnyis pa rdzas kyi de nyid bstan pa ni /
NK036(chi)012:257: bum pa lnga ru byung ba ni rig pa lnga rang la rdzoogs pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:258: shel lnga ni gzhi ka nas dag pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:259: rma bya'i mdongs lnga ni sgron ma lnga rang la gsal ba'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:260: mda' lnga ni shes rab lnga mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:261: me long lnga ni ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:262: dar sna lnga ni rlung lnga mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:263: phur pa lnga ni dbyings rnam par dag pa la 'gyur ba med pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:264: ral gri lnga ni mngal gyi grong khyer 'joms pa'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:265: tshogs gtor dang mchod pa ni 'dod yon rang sprul du shar ba'i barda'o //
NK036(chi)012:266: gnyis pa byin rlabs slob dpon gyi bya ba la bzhi las /
NK036(chi)012:267: dang po bum pa'i dbang dang gcig /
NK036(chi)012:269: gsum pa shesaraba ye shes kyi dbang /
NK036(chi)012:270: bzhi pa nges pa tshig don ngo sprod kyi dbang ngo //
NK036(chi)012:271: de la dang po ni slob ma rnams lus gnad
NK036(chi)012:272: rdo rje skyil krung 'char bcug bla mas dbus kyi
NK036(chi)012:274: slob bu'i spyir bor bzhag nas /
NK036(chi)012:276: chos nyid dbyings kyi bum pa ru //
NK036(chi)012:277: stong gsal rang byung chu yis bkang //
NK036(chi)012:278: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:279: dbyings kyi gnas lugs rtogs par shog /
NK036(chi)012:280: k+aa li'i yi ge'i tshogs brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK036(chi)012:281: spyi bo'i rtsa gnas kyi yi ge rnams brjod la dbang bskur te /
NK036(chi)012:293: pa p+aa na zhes pas khrus bya /
NK036(chi)012:294: spyi bor chu thigs pa blug go //
NK036(chi)012:295: de nas shar gyi bu ma pa blangs la snying gar bzhag ste /
NK036(chi)012:297: ma skyes snying po'i bum pa ru //
NK036(chi)012:298: 'gag med rang byung rdzas kyis bkang //
NK036(chi)012:299: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:300: 'jigs bral bzhi yi don rtogs shog /
NK036(chi)012:301: ces pas +aa li'i rjes la dran pa 'dus pa'i rtsa yig rnams brjod la dbang bskur ro //
NK036(chi)012:302: kha tsa ta ta pha la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK036(chi)012:303: ka g+h+aab+h+aa dz+ha zhes pas snying gar chu'i thig le bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:304: de nas lho'i bum pa btegs la mgrin par gtad la /
NK036(chi)012:306: rang byung ye shes bum pa ru //
NK036(chi)012:307: 'dod yon rang sprul rdzas kyis bkang //
NK036(chi)012:308: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:309: bsam pa lhun grub dbang thob shog /
NK036(chi)012:311: +aa li'i rjes la de rnams 'dus pa'i rtsa yig rnams brjod la dbang bskur te /
NK036(chi)012:316: zhes brjod la chu thigs gcig blud do //
NK036(chi)012:317: de nas nub kyi bum pa bteg ste /
NK036(chi)012:319: ma skyes chags bral bum pa ru //
NK036(chi)012:320: bde chen rgyun spro'i rdzas kyis bkang //
NK036(chi)012:321: skal ldan khyed la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:322: chags pa 'dzin med dbang thob shog /
NK036(chi)012:323: +aa li'i rjes la skyed byed kyi rtsa yig rnams brjod de dbang bskur la /
NK036(chi)012:325: ta li ha u nya ram yam nam na dzi
NK036(chi)012:326: ta pa kham yam ram na dzi ta pa kham
NK036(chi)012:327: yam ram / zhes lte bar chu'i thig le bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:328: de nas byang gi bum pa bteg la gnas bzhir
NK036(chi)012:329: byug cing +aa li k+aa la'i rjes la 'khor lo
NK036(chi)012:330: sogs bzhi ka'i rtsa yig brjod de /
NK036(chi)012:332: ye shes zang thal bum pa ru //
NK036(chi)012:333: 'gags med rlung lnga'i rdzas kyis bkang //
NK036(chi)012:334: skal ldan khyed la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:335: rang byung rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK036(chi)012:336: de nas de rnams kyi tshig gi don yang bshad par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:337: gnyis pa gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK036(chi)012:338: ka p+aa la bdud rtsi chang gis bkang ba de btegs la /
NK036(chi)012:339: gnas bzhir bzhag cing slob ma rnams gong bzhin lus gnad bcas la /
NK036(chi)012:340: gnas bzhi'i rang bzhin gyi kun bzang yab yum sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas /
NK036(chi)012:341: de dag gi byang sems kyis rtsa gnas dang lus
NK036(chi)012:342: gang bas bde ba chen po'i ngang la gnas par
NK036(chi)012:344: bde chen brdal ba rang byung ka p+aa la //
NK036(chi)012:345: chags pa dngos dag kun bzang thig les bkang //
NK036(chi)012:346: rigs chen skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK036(chi)012:347: rtsa rlung byang sems mchog la dbang thob shog /
NK036(chi)012:348: ces pa dang +aa li'i rjes la 'khor lo bzhi'i yi ge brjod la tshig don yang bshad do //
NK036(chi)012:349: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK036(chi)012:350: las rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la 'khyud la /
NK036(chi)012:353: snang srid bde chen brdal ba'i zhing khams la //
NK036(chi)012:354: rol pa'i ye shes bde ba chen por shar //
NK036(chi)012:355: thabs shes 'dod pa spyod pas grol gyur te //
NK036(chi)012:356: ma 'gags rol pa spyod cing bde ba che //
NK036(chi)012:357: zhes pas dngos su sbyar bas chags pa'i pra khrid ltar bde ba bskyed do //
NK036(chi)012:358: bzhi pa tshig don ngo sprod kyi dbang ni /
NK036(chi)012:359: brda'i don nyid kyis bstan par bya ste /
NK036(chi)012:360: skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob bu khyod nyon cig /
NK036(chi)012:361: nam mkha'i dbyings na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la /
NK036(chi)012:362: nyi zla gnyis shar nas 'dug pa mthong ngam /
NK036(chi)012:364: bar snang gi 'ja' tshon la rlung gi zhags pas btab nas 'dug pa mthong ngam /
NK036(chi)012:365: rgya mtsho'i nor bu shel gyi rta pho la zhon
NK036(chi)012:366: nas nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du dkyus thag gcod pa
NK036(chi)012:367: de mthong ngam / 'byung lnga'i grong khyer du rigs
NK036(chi)012:368: drug gi dmag mi bcug nas ri rab kyi steng
NK036(chi)012:369: du song ba'i mi dang khams gsum gyi 'phrang la
NK036(chi)012:370: shel gyi mi pho btson du bzung ba de mthong
NK036(chi)012:371: de mthong ngam / ngam / khams gsum skad cig
NK036(chi)012:372: la bskor nas rang gi khyim du gnyid du song
NK036(chi)012:374: zhes brda'i don bzhi dkrol nas tshig 'di bstan par bya ste /
NK036(chi)012:376: ma yengs gson cig rigs kyi bu //
NK036(chi)012:378: rten 'brel gyi 'char sgo ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:379: don dam tshig gis mi rtogs kyang //
NK036(chi)012:380: mngon sum la gding thob ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:381: rig pa la skye 'bri med mod kyang //
NK036(chi)012:382: lam snang gi 'char tshul ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:383: ka dag la grol rgyu ma mchis kyang //
NK036(chi)012:384: rlung rig gi dag tshul ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:385: theg pa'i 'jug sgo mang mod kyang //
NK036(chi)012:386: cig car du thob pa ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:387: shes tshul gyi snang ba rgya che yang //
NK036(chi)012:388: ngo bo la gding thob ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:389: tshig mtha' la spros pa mang mod kyang //
NK036(chi)012:390: brda' gcig gis don mthong ngo mtshar che //
NK036(chi)012:391: zhes pa'i rdo rje'i glu yis bskul lo //
NK036(chi)012:392: de nas dpa' bo pho tshogs dang mo tshogs dga' ston chen pos mchod /
NK036(chi)012:393: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong gtor mas mchod do //
NK036(chi)012:394: rjes 'od gsal sgyu ma lta bu la gnas par bya'o //
NK036(chi)012:395: spros bcas dbang la tshig don rgya che ba //
NK036(chi)012:396: tshig la nyung zhing don la chad med pa //
NK036(chi)012:397: lag len dam pa'i phyag bzhes 'dir bkod pa //
NK036(chi)012:398: 'dir 'jug smin pas 'gro ba bde thob shog /
NK036(chi)012:399: spros bcas dbang gi phyag bzhes /
NK036(chi)012:400: dang po'i dpe las lag len khrigs su sdebs pa /
NK036(chi)012:401: lce btsun seng ge dbang phyug gis mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK036(chi)012:402: sngags kyi srung mas srungs shig /
NK036(chi)012:403: skal ldan cig dang phrad par shog /
NK036(chi)012:410: rdzong kha ba rgyal ba blo gros /
NK036(chi)012:411: bla ma kun dga' don grub /
